
/* BEFORE AUTOMATION (MVP)
* Gamepad 1:
*
* Left Joystick X and Y - strafe (drive)
* Right Joystick X - turn (drive)
*
* Left Joystick Button -
* Right Joystick Button -
*
* Left Bumper - stop intake and flip up
* Right Bumper - start intake and flip down
*
* Left Trigger - retract horizontal slide (acts like joystick, not automatically to a set distance)
* Right Trigger - extend horizontal slides
*
* A - toggle extend to high basket and retract (slides)
* B - toggle claw
* Y - slow mode (drive)
* X - toggle arm
*
* D-Pad Up - full intake process (start, check for color and/or eject, stop)
* D-Pad Down - navx reset (drive)
* D-Pad Left -
* D-Pad Right -
*
*/

/* VINCENT'S PREFERENCE
* Gamepad 1:
*
* Left Joystick X and Y - strafe (drive)
* Right Joystick X - turn (drive)
*
* Left Joystick Button - slow turn
* Right Joystick Button - slow strafe
*
* Left Bumper - claw toggle
* Right Bumper - start intake and flip down, otherwise flip up and stop
*
* Left Trigger - slowmode (when >0.5, 30% speed)
* Right Trigger - extend horizontal slides to mapped distance
*                 (ex: 1 -> 100%, 0.5 -> 80%, 0.1 -> 60%, 0 -> 0%)
*
* A - high basket slide toggle
* B - toggle arm
* Y - hang (NOT DONE, WORK ON)
* X - medium basket slide toggle
*
* D-Pad Up - full intake process (start, check for color and/or eject, stop)
* D-Pad Down - navx reset (drive)
* D-Pad Left - secondary hang release
* D-Pad Right -
*
* D-Pad Right & Right Bumper - reverse intake/eject
*
*/





/* AFTER AUTOMATION
*
* Gamepad 1:
*
* Left Joystick X and Y - strafe (drive)
* Right Joystick X - turn (drive)
*
* Left Bumper -
* Right Bumper -
*
* Left trigger -
* Right trigger -
*
* A - auto-extend intake, then retract once picked up piece (scoring)
* B - vertical slide extend, then deposit, then retract (scoring)
* Y - slow mode toggle (drive)
* X - reset gyro (drive)
*
* D-Pad Up -
* D-Pad Down -
* D-Pad Left -
* D-Pad Right -
*

